## Setup Instructions

1. Import the database file `ticket_system.sql` into MySQL
2. Update database credentials in `config.php`
3. Start your local server (XAMPP/WAMP)
4. Navigate to `http://localhost/ticket-system`

## Features Implemented

- User authentication (login/logout)
- Ticket creation and management
- Filter tickets by Issue Type, Priority, and Date
- Real-time search with autocomplete suggestions
- Edit and delete tickets
- Responsive navbar with dropdown menus

## Known Issues

- Search suggestions may overlap with table on smaller screens
- Date filter needs timezone adjustment
- Clear All Filters button doesn't show when only one filter is active